    "By supervised integration of these rich and structured resources, the capabilities of PLM will be significantly enhanced (Öztürk et al., 2019; Doğan et al., 2021).",
    "In addition, the introduction of additional resources such as physical world simulations provided by the field of molecular dynamics (MD) will greatly deepen our understanding of molecular behavior and interactions.",
    "The organic integration of PLM with MD not only complements PLM's strengths in data processing but also strengthens its ability to analyze complex scientific phenomena, allowing for finer and more accurate interpretations (Zhang et al., 2024).",
    "In terms of coding strategies, the traditional linear positional coding can be replaced by introducing biologically relevant positional information, such as the distance matrix and contact map between sequences, to better model long-distance dependencies.",
    "Frontiers in Bioengineering and Biotechnology frontiersin.org"
